snippet: Harry Styles, Bradley Cooper and Naomie Harris led an all-star front row Monday at Burberry Prorsum's runway show, a display featuring luxurious painted jackets and thick wool blankets....

headline.print_headline: Harry Styles, Bradley Cooper Front Row at Burberry
headline.main: Harry Styles, Bradley Cooper Front Row at Burberry

lead_paragraph: Harry Styles, Bradley Cooper and Naomie Harris led an all-star front row Monday at Burberry Prorsum's runway show, a display featuring luxurious painted jackets and thick wool blankets.
